<DOCID> 248183 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 17, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Calendar; Part F; Page 2; Column 2; Entertainment Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
