WEST GERMANY; REUNIFICATION; NORTH ATLANTIC TREATY ORGANIZATION; GERMANY -- 
ARMED FORCES; GORBACHEV, MIKHAIL S; KOHL, HELMUT; EUROPE -- SECURITY; USSR -- 
ARMED FORCES -- EAST GERMANY; UNITED STATES -- ARMED FORCES; GERMANY -- ARMED 
FORCES 
</P>
