FRANCE; ENGLAND -- GOVERNMENT OFFICIALS; RIDLEY, NICHOLAS; RESIGNATIONS; 
EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES; EUROPEAN UNIFICATION; THATCHER, MARGARET; EUROPE -- 
