the AFL its brightest moment, leading the New York Jets to victory in Super 
Bowl III as 18-point underdogs. ; Photo, Lamar Hunt decided to help start the 
American Football League in 1960 after the NFL wouldn't sell him a franchise 
for Dallas. 
</P>
