<P>
ORANGE COUNTY -- POLITICS; REPUBLICAN PARTY (ORANGE COUNTY); NIXON, RICHARD M; 
PRESIDENTIAL LIBRARIES; CALIFORNIA -- ELECTIONS; LEGISLATORS -- ORANGE COUNTY; 
CONSERVATISM 
