FAMILIES; CHILDREN; COMMUNITY SERVICE PROGRAMS; SHELTERS; PARTIES; RONALD 
MCDONALD CHILDREN'S CHARITIES; FUND RAISING 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA071790-0152 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 248594 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
July 17, 1990, Tuesday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
View; Part E; Page 3; Column 4; View Desk 
</P>
