dark," he told reporters. In one recent incident 18 officials spent four hours 
chasing one group of children who escaped untouched. 
</P>
<P>
The animated television series, which is screened daily in Australia, features 
mutant turtles who live in the sewers and fight crime using ninja martial arts. 
