<P>
Profile 
</P>
</TYPE>
<SUBJECT>
<P>
FOOTBALL PLAYERS; AMERICAN FOOTBALL LEAGUE; UNITED STATES -- GOVERNMENT 
OFFICIALS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
