Photo, Rep. Nixon views film during investigation of Alger Hiss. ; Photo, The 
famous Checkers speech. ; Photo, Nixon, Nikita Khrushchev tangle during kitchen 
debate. ; Photo, After conceding defeat in '62. ; Photo, Waves to crowd after 
his inauguration in 1968. ; Photo, Meeting with Mao Tse-tung. ; Photo, 
Protesters in Washington. ; Photo, Above, Nixon announces resignation. Below, 
loyal followers await his return to Southland. ; Photo, Nixon departs with 
David Frost after agreeing to interview. 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
